<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nḥw ḥḍnk ạlrḥym</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - nḥw ḥḍnk ạlrḥyl ạ̉jry ạ̉rtmy
 ạ̉lqy kẖwfy ạ̉lqy tẖqly qyd mʿṣmy
 ạ̹dẖạ fy jnbk ạljryḥ ybrạ̉ mạ̉tẖmy
 wfy ṣdrk ạlrḥyb bạlḥb ạ̉ḥtmy
 1- dwnk ḍʿyf jỷt fy ạlmsyḥ
 fạ̉rsẖdny fy ṭryqy̱ yạ kẖyr ạlmsẖyr
 qd ḥmlt kl ḥzny fwq kạtfy wrfʿt ʿny ậtẖmy ʿnd ṣlbk
 yạ gẖbạỷy qd ḥsbt hdẖạ dẖnbk whw dẖnb ậtẖm jhly qd ạgẖḍbtk
 qd sẖfyt yạ qdyr kl mn ạ̉sạʾ fy ạ̉ymạn jạʾ yrjw
 kl dạʾ qd msḥt fy nʿym wrḥym qd gẖfrt dẖnby yạ krym</lyrics>
<author>fhym ạ̉dyb, bhyr ạ̹dwạrd</author>
<hymn_number>2461</hymn_number>
</song>